 
<p>

The Group of 7 wealthiest countries are converging on a policy
of <a href="https://www.commondreams.org/news/lng-g7-summit-japan">increasing extraction of methane for fuel</a>.  This will speed up
climate disaster.
<p>
  Activists are <a href="https://www.commondreams.org/newswire/100-organizations-urge-biden-administration-to-stop-g7-push-for-lng-expansion">calling on Biden to stop this</a>.
  Biden is not the most steadfast and reliable of champions for
climate defense.  The sad thing is that there is no one else to appeal
to.

 